## 🧪 測試驗證指令

### 本地測試指令
```bash
# 端口可用性測試
netstat -ano | findstr :8080     # Windows檢查端口
lsof -i :8080                    # Linux/Mac檢查端口

# 服務可用性測試
curl http://localhost:8080       # 基本連接測試
curl -I http://localhost:8080    # 檢查響應頭

# WebSocket測試
curl --include \
     --no-buffer \
     --header "Connection: Upgrade" \
     --header "Upgrade: websocket" \
     --header "Sec-WebSocket-Key: SGVsbG8sIHdvcmxkIQ==" \
     --header "Sec-WebSocket-Version: 13" \
     http://localhost:8080/
```

### 功能測試指令
```bash
# AI助教功能測試
node test-ai.js              # 如果有測試腳本
npm test                     # 運行測試套件

# 數據庫連接測試
node -e "
const mysql = require('mysql2');
const connection = mysql.createConnection({
  host: process.env.MYSQL_HOST,
  user: process.env.MYSQL_USER,
  password: process.env.MYSQL_PASSWORD
});
connection.connect(err => {
  console.log(err ? '❌ 連接失敗' : '✅ 連接成功');
  connection.end();
});
"
```

### 性能測試指令
```bash
# 記憶體使用監控
node -e "
setInterval(() => {
  const used = process.memoryUsage();
  console.log(\`記憶體使用: \${Math.round(used.heapUsed / 1024 / 1024)} MB\`);
}, 5000);
"

# 負載測試 (如果安裝了artillery)
artillery quick --count 10 --num 100 http://localhost:8080
```

